Covert Skins.name: AK-47 | Nightwish
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a deer and dreamcatchers in neon colors and finished with a pearlescent effect.
Covert Skins.lore: I've been saving this for a special occasion... – Booth, Arms Dealer

Covert Skins.name: MP9 | Starlight Protector
Covert Skins.desc: This custom paint job features a unicorn with a rainbow mane atop a white base. It has been finished with gold accents.
Covert Skins.lore: May the deity protect you, should the deity select you

Classified Skins.name: FAMAS | Rapid Eye Movement
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with pink interlocking squares. The squares are painted with lifelike eyes.
Classified Skins.lore: Frantic are the eyes of the dreamer

Classified Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Melondrama
Classified Skins.desc: These berettas have been custom painted with a twisted, frightening depiction of a watermelon over a navy blue background.

Classified Skins.name: MP7 | Abyssal Apparition
Classified Skins.desc: This custom paint job depicts abandoned souls falling into a pit of nightmares.

Restricted Skins.name: USP-S | Ticket to Hell
Restricted Skins.desc: White technical designs have been custom painted over a black base.

Restricted Skins.name: XM1014 | Zombie Offensive
Restricted Skins.desc: A custom pattern of zombified Counter-Strike agents has been applied.

Restricted Skins.name: M4A1-S | Night Terror
Restricted Skins.desc: Scattered thoughts from the mind of an insomniac have been scrawled across this custom-painted A1-S.
Restricted Skins.lore: In the bosom of the gentle night, is when I search for the light

Restricted Skins.name: PP-Bizon | Space Cat
Restricted Skins.desc: A space art depiction of a cat has been custom painted over a black and purple base.

Restricted Skins.name: G3SG1 | Dream Glade
Restricted Skins.desc: A green forest gives way to a blue sky at the center of this custom paint job.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAC-10 | Ensnared
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A custom paint job of pixies, trapped inside the weapon and eager to escape, has been applied.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: They have yet to find someone they cannot fool

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MP5-SD | Necro Jr.
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with fairytale inspired creatures and a chicken on the silencer.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Sawed-Off | Spirit Board
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to resemble a heavily played spirit board.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: "Come on, I know you're moving it..."

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P2000 | Lifted Spirits
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a forest beneath ascending bodies.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Many lost souls do not wish to be found

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SCAR-20 | Poultrygeist
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been spray-painted with a pattern depicting chickens on a battlefield.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: A chicken rides a shark into battle...

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Five-SeveN | Scrawl
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Custom designs have been hand-painted using bold strokes over a yellow and teal base.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAG-7 | Foresight
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: This custom paint job features an octopus, asked to predict the outcome of a match, reaching for the "win" tablet.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: I've got a good feeling about this...
